== 學術研究與教學 ==
{{Infobox world university ranking| ARWU_W = 57 | ARWU_W_ref = <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2020.html|title=ARWU World University Rankings 2020 - Academic Ranking of World Universities 2020 - Top 500 universities - Shanghai Ranking - 2020|author=|date=|website=www.shanghairanking.com|accessdate=2019-05-20|archive-date=2018-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180816224432/http://www.shanghairanking.com/ARWU2020.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>| THE_W = 42 | THE_W_ref = <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2021/world-ranking|title=World University Rankings|author=|date=1 November 2018|website=timeshighereducation.com|accessdate=2019-05-20|archive-date=2018-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021113908/https://www.timeshighereducation.com/world-university-rankings/2021/world-ranking|dead-url=no}}</ref>| QS_W = 64 | QS_W_ref = <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2021|title=QS World University Rankings 2021|author=|date=1 November 2018|website=topuniversities.com|accessdate=2019-05-20|archive-date=2018-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608073254/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/world-university-rankings/2021|dead-url=no}}</ref>| USNWR_W = 54 | USNWR_W_ref = <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings?page=6|title=U.S. News Education: Best Global Universities 2020|author=|date=1 November 2018|website=usnews.com|accessdate=2019-05-20|archive-date=2019-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404111512/https://www.usnews.com/education/best-global-universities/rankings?page=6|dead-url=no}}</ref>
